					USA 2016				


						February 29 – March 4					

						Moscone Center, San Francisco					











Security First Corp.




					Security First Corp. is a pioneer of software-defined data-centric security, high-availability and business continuity solutions based on their highly-patented SPx™ Technology. SPx takes security beyond traditional network security solutions by protecting data at its core no matter where it’s stored (network attached, public, private, hybrid-cloud), while ensuring its integrity.				


						New Product
					

SPxGateway™


						SPxGateway™ is the solution for easy access to cloud object storage reinforced by the security of SPx™ technology and cloud spanning capabilities. It installs as a virtual appliance in an existing virtual infrastructure, and allows companies to leverage low-cost, highly scalable storage in the cloud.

Key features of SPxGateway include:
•	Secured by SPx technology
•	Split data to multiple cloud providers simultaneously
•	High availability regardless of disaster or center outage
•	Cloud vendor operates in a Zero Knowledge environment
•	Utilization for primary backup, archive, or cloud storage
•	Lossless compression
•	Snapshots
•	Dynamic volume sizing
•	Dynamic cache
•	Cloud cache for local access to recent files
•	Simplified, on-premise key management
•	Simple Network Management Protocol (SNMP) integration
•	Identity and Access Management (IDAM) solution integration
•	Block level storage
•	File level storage					




